                    SimCity DEMO NOTICES:
THE DEMO:The DEMO loops every 3 minutes or so.  Any player input will abort the
current pass through the demo, and allow the playing of SimCity.  The Simulator
will only run for 3 minutes in this version.  If the DEMO is interrupted, it
will be restarted after 1 minute of with no user input.  The PRINT, SAVE, and
LOAD menu options are disabled for the DEMO.

CURSOR CONTROL: With the PS/2 & BUS type mouse interfaces, the keyboard
mouse-emulation has been disabled.

COVOX CARD and the PS/2 MOUSE: If you are using a PS/2 type mouse interface,
you cannot use the COVOX card with SimCity.

INSTALLATION: You need to install this demo onto a hard disk.
